{"lemma":"أَوْرِدَةُ","slug":"أَوْرِدَةُ","root":"#.ر.د","root_slug":"_-ر-د","root_link":"/words/roots/_-ر-د","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":true,"lemma_key":"وَرِيد","root":"ورد","pos":"N","occurrence_count":1},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n41851"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%A3%D9%8E%D9%88%D9%92%D8%B1%D9%90%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%A9%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"vein"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"jugular vein"}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"From the root و ر د (w r d). Compare وَتِين (watīn, “aorta”) and Akkadian 𒌨𒌑𒁺 (ur'udu, “windpipe, throat veins”)."},"ipa":["/wa.riːd/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n41851","headword_ar":"اوردهُ","root":"wrd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Astwrdhu","text_ar":"استوردهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"twr~dhu","text_ar":"تورّدهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (ISd,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought him to the watering-place."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  Also, the first and second of these verbs,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought him; made him to come,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to be present."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L.) ―         -b3-  [And the first,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He adduced it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"cited it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, an evidence, a speech or saying, a word, &c. ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He set it forth,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"expressed it;"},{"kind":"text","text":"namely, a meaning.] ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Awrdhu","text_ar":"اوردهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaA='a","text_ar":"المَا=ءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_iyraAdN","text_ar":"اـِيرَادٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", A.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to come to the water."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, Msb.) [See an ex. voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HamoDN","text_ar":"حَمْضٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".] ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Awrdhu AlD~alaAlapa","text_ar":"اوردهُ الضَّلَالَةَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made him to run into error."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aworada Ealayohi xayorFA","text_ar":"اَوْرَدَ عَلَيْهِ خَيْرًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought to him wealth, property,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"what was good."},{"kind":"text","text":"] (Mugh, in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HTb","text_ar":"حطب"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Awrd Ealayohi Alxabara","text_ar":"اورد عَلَيْهِ الخَبَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He related to him the news."},{"kind":"text","text":"(L.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Awrd Al$~aYo'a","text_ar":"اورد الشَّىْءَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He mentioned the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^worada wA^aSodara","text_ar":"اوْرَدَ واَصْدَرَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He began and compelled."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA, art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sdr","text_ar":"صدر"},{"kind":"text","text":") ―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Awrdh","text_ar":"اورده"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wASdrh","text_ar":"واصدره"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He brought it and he took it away."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har. p. 